I DIDN'T LOVE.

00:01:03.830 --> 00:01:05.933
- YEAH.
- BUT ENOUGH ABOUT ME.

00:01:05.966 --> 00:01:08.335
SHOOT.
- I-I DON'T KNOW HOW TO PLAY.

00:01:08.368 --> 00:01:10.971
