CLOSE YOUR EYES,

00:01:21.815 --> 00:01:23.750
AND PUT IT IN.

00:01:23.784 --> 00:01:25.586
- IS EVERYTHING OKAY
IN HERE?

00:01:25.619 --> 00:01:29.656
- IT'S FINE, MARK.
JUST FINE.

00:01:29.690 --> 00:01:31.692
WHY DON'T WE GO SOMEWHERE
WHERE WE CAN BE

00:01:31.725 --> 00:01:32.926
A LITTLE MORE PRIVATE?

00:01:32.960 --> 00:01:34.494
